data.description: Stunning 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 2 story home located in the sought after neighborhood of the Trellises at Embassy Lakes. Open floorplan with oversized tile in the main living area and wood laminate floors throughout the bedrooms and stairs. Walk in closets in all bedrooms with master located on the first floor. Kitchen has wood cabinets and granite countertops with stainless steel appliances. 2014 tile roof, tankless water heater, Fence, Landscaping, Garage door all from 2021/22. Garage features washer/dryer and 220 electric car outlet New light fixtures and blink security system with Accordion shutters included! The newly enclosed patio and fence allow for maximum privacy. Multiple amenities including tennis, gym, pool, playgrounds and tennis court. Plus, the best A rated schools around!
